ActVeterans Review and Appeal Board Act
PrecisAppointment of OWEN J.W. PARKHOUSE of Morell, Prince Edward Island, to be a permanent member of the Veterans Review and Appeal Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and designate OWEN J.W. PARKHOUSE as interim Deputy Chairperson until such time as a new Deputy Chair is appointed.
